message.text:
𝓣𝓱𝓮 𝓢𝓽𝓻𝓮𝓮𝓽 𝓕𝓲𝓵𝓵𝓮𝓭 𝔀𝓲𝓽𝓱 𝓤𝓷𝓯𝓸𝓻𝓰𝓮𝓽𝓽𝓪𝓫𝓵𝓮 𝓜𝓮𝓶𝓸𝓻𝓲𝓮𝓼  ✨

Thank you HospitaliTAMs for joining us as we took a stroll around the scenic views of Bataan. You were there as we filled another chapter in our elegant and timeless story. As we start another journey let’s look back upon our stay at the Las Casas. 

The HRM Society welcomes all our new members and we appreciate you taking the opportunity to mark your presence among these historical streets.

message.text:
𝓣𝓱𝓮 𝓢𝓽𝓻𝓮𝓮𝓽 𝓕𝓲𝓵𝓵𝓮𝓭 𝔀𝓲𝓽𝓱 𝓤𝓷𝓯𝓸𝓻𝓰𝓮𝓽𝓽𝓪𝓫𝓵𝓮 𝓜𝓮𝓶𝓸𝓻𝓲𝓮𝓼  ✨

Thank you HospitaliTAMs for joining us as we took a stroll around the scenic views of Bataan. You were there as we filled another chapter in our elegant and timeless story. As we start another journey let’s look back upon our stay at the Las Casas. 

The HRM Society welcomes all our new members and we appreciate you taking the opportunity to mark your presence among these historical streets.

𝑺𝒐, 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒅𝒚 𝒕𝒐 𝒋𝒐𝒊𝒏 𝒖𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒏𝒆𝒘 𝒄𝒉𝒂𝒑𝒕𝒆𝒓? 🤎💛

Caption by: Jayden Javier 
Poster by: Brian Coscolluela 

#HRMSociety
 #HusayTalentoAtSerbisyo
 #LasCasasDeHospitalismo

Tuloy ang pagtubo. Tuloy ang pagtahak! 🌾 
Face-to-face TamHunt ended, pero hindi pa kami tapos. ✊ Peace continues to grow and bloom because of dedicated changemakers!

Tuloy ang taniman. Tuloy ang kwento. Sama ka na samin? 🌿 APPLY Peace TAYO! 🤎🌾
